        <cdata>
          <text>&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;School Guardian Act of 2023&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This bill requires the Department of Justice (DOJ) to make grants for states to assign armed law enforcement officers to provide security at elementary and secondary schools.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The bill also requires specified unobligated Internal Revenue Service funds to be transferred to DOJ to implement this bill.&lt;/p&gt;</text>
        </cdata>
      </summary>
